sentences: Following the band's separation in 1994, she and Tribe guitarist Eric Brosius married.
Brosius and her husband, along with Tribe bass player Greg LoPiccolo, joined video game developer Looking Glass Studios, where they worked on various game projects until its closure in 2000.
System Shock – CD enhanced version (1994) (also writer)
The Metal Age (2000) (also writer, level designer)
Spider: Rite of the Shrouded Moon (2015) (also writer)
Terri is currently a keyboardist and backup vocalist for the Boston-based band The Vivs.
